Yes comport411c works fine on Delphi Berlin 10.1.

    In your Delphi Berlin 10.1, Library Path, add these 2 Paths :
    ...\ComPort\comport411\DCU
    ...\ComPort\comport411\Source

    Open : CPortLibDXE.dproj
    On your Project Manager, click Right on CPortLibDXE.Bpl --> Compile and Build it.

    Open : DsgnCPortDXE.dpk
    On your Project Manager, click Right on DsgnCPortDXE.Bpl --> Compile and Build and Install it.

it will install the components.
Best Regards.